title: Double Greeting Wonton House
typeOfFood: Ovo, Chinese, Fast food, Take-out, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Hong Kong style diner. Menu has a large vegetarian section with various vegan suitable dishes, such as the ginger and green onion lo-mein (item 44), bean curd with mixed vegetables (211), kai-lan with garlic (226), vermicelli Singapore style (322), pan fried noodles with bean sprouts (328), among others. Ask which noodles are egg-less.
